MOST people who love travelling to other countries know that enjoying the culture of that place makes for great memories. But what happens when one of the places, like a hotel you’d expect to be safe in, turns out to be your worst nightmare? In tonight’s movie, terror strikes as Lashkar-e-Taiba members storm the Taj Mahal Palace Hotel in India. Amid the mayhem, a brave chef and kitchen worker risk their lives to try and protect the frightened guests.